{"tid":2231580,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友打電話比分手後變成綠茶婊既前女友","createTime":"2020-10-05T18:11:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T18:55:57.000Z","uid":198411,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f52c9c43a64c33963233eb137370c1a8d28a2b04","tid":2231580,"uid":198411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T18:11:39.000Z","msg":"我同男朋友交友app識，一齊係因為大家都曾經有過一段好深既感情，感同身受，一齊互相慰藉<br />\n<br />\n以下簡稱我bf = bf, 我bf ex= ex<br />\nbf同一齊左幾年既ex分手，近日佢從友人口中得知，ex與bf分手後居然向我同佢另一位共同朋友既男友示愛，搶人男朋友，我bf聽到之後就勁嬲，依幾日都冇乜理我，見面都淨係講佢，仲見佢手機打左好多次133比佢，我問佢點解佢打比佢，佢就話想質問佢點解作賤自己，但一直都打唔通，仲話想去打獲比ex搶左果個朋友既男朋友。<br />\n<br />\n我聽完覺得好頹，一齊左都幾個月，bf都仲係諗住分左手幾年個ex⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家諗到bf同佢ex都覺得好煩，應唔應該分手？<br />\nbtw sorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"539a3dcd8c99dcdb40e4fcb5ace191e4e2b575db","tid":2231580,"uid":47222,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T18:12:45.000Z","msg":"支那用語 拉"},{"pid":"d5733a28291136643aeb0b7f954bc794b19cde69","tid":2231580,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"539a3dcd8c99dcdb40e4fcb5ace191e4e2b575db","tid":2231580,"uid":47222,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T18:12:45.000Z","msg":"支那用語 拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T18:13:22.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"7be21376888f7e42c89da56be34abbc000c2b90a","tid":2231580,"uid":62337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T18:15:34.000Z","msg":"你條仔對咩女都有興趣架啦<br />\n你水泡黎咋醒未"},{"pid":"c82501802ee7fc1720490e8166b9c95d1506de91","tid":2231580,"uid":90441,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T18:51:14.000Z","msg":"臭雞就臭雞啦  乜撚野綠茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286755c1ee7d05929841e289993bb7b845e19492","tid":2231580,"uid":3008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T18:55:57.000Z","msg":"我係條仔就飛咗你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"